  1. SET-1091
  2. SET-1018

Spike to investigate the project size of building duplicate treatments in haml

Description

Italic On

🤔 Problem Description:

Provide a description of the issue

The treatments & classes redesign project size is so large that this will likely not be completed until 2024. Breaking off a small part of this project will help deliver value to users now. Treatment duplicate is one of the highest voted onboarding related feature requests in canny. With new treatment and class types (Telehealth & Group apps) and our expansion into markets that need to create a high number of services (aesthetics) the need to create long lists of treatments with only a few differences in settings between services the need for this feature has grown.

  • We need to define the size of dev work for this project to confirm that it’s worth building in haml before treatments is redesigned in React

ℹ️ Task:

How should this feature work?

  • Minimal design changes to the treatments settings page.

  • The only design change to the page will be to add a duplicate button besides the edit button

  • Recreate the duplicate code that exists on the intake forms page on the treatments & classes settings page.

  • Duplicate treatments should mimic the behaviour of the existing duplicate intake forms feature.

ℹ️ Criteria & Requirements:

Provide detailed information as to how the function should work.

  • Investigate the amount of dev work required to build this feature

  • Identify potential blockers and constraints that would prevent us from recreating the intake duplication feature on the treatments page.

Spike findings.


Based on the intake form duplicate feature the following work would likely need to be implemented:

1. A controller definition for “duplicate”
https://github.com/janeapp/jane/blob/master/app/controllers/admin/intake_forms_controller.rb#L107C11-L107C11

2. role.rb permissions would need to be added
https://github.com/janeapp/jane/blob/master/app/models/role.rb

3. For the actual button: app/views/admin/intake_forms/index.html.haml
https://github.com/janeapp/jane/blob/master/app/views/admin/intake_forms/index.html.haml#L50

4. Routes?
https://github.com/janeapp/jane/blob/master/config/routes.rb#L1189

5. Intakes has some permissions defined as a policy (Pundit?) but these would be better defined in the ability.rb file for our purposes.

app/policies/intake_form_policy.rb:
https://github.com/janeapp/jane/blob/master/app/policies/intake_form_policy.rb#L60

6. Tests!


Questions:
Access-- would we want everyone who can access treatments to be able to duplicate them?
Noting that there are some access levels that cannot access treatments from Settings, but can access it from their own profile (to see their treatments only) should those access levels be able to to duplicate treatments?
